a1 = ("TERMINATOR 2: JUDGMENT DAY\nSYNOPSIS: When a child destined to be a leader is born, he is deprived of the company of his mother, who was considered insane when she spoke of a Terminator coming from the future. In this context, another android appears to kill the child.\nAUTHOR: James Cameron and William Wisher Jr.\nAVAILABLE IN: Youtube and Google Play")
