a3 = ("X-MEN: DAYS OF FUTURE PAST\nSYNOPSIS: In the future, mutants are mercilessly hunted by the gigantic Sentinels. The few survivors must live in hiding, otherwise they will also be killed. They seek a way to prevent mutants from being annihilated. To do so, they need to send Wolverine's consciousness on a journey through time, towards the 1970s. There, he seeks out the still young Xavier and Magneto so that, together, they can prevent this tragic future for mutants from becoming a reality.\nAUTHOR: Chris Claremont.\nAVAILABLE IN: Disney+")
a4 = ("GUARDIANS OF THE GALAXY\nSYNOPSIS: Peter Quill (Chris Pratt) was abducted from Earth as a child. As an adult, he made a career out of marauding and earned the name Star-Lord. When he steals an orb, in which the powerful villain Ronan, of the Kree race, is interested, he becomes sought after by several bounty hunters. To escape danger, Quill joins forces with four out-of-system characters: Groot, a humanoid tree (Vin Diesel), the dark and dangerous Gamora (Zoe Saldana), the trigger-happy raccoon Rocket Racoon (Bradley Cooper) and the vengeful Drax. , the Destroyer (Dave Bautista). But Star-Lord discovers that the stolen sphere has a power capable of changing the course of the universe, and soon the group must protect the object to save the future of the galaxy.\nAUTHOR: Dan Abnett, Andy Lanning\nAVAILABLE IN: Disney+")
a5 = ("JURASSIC WORLD: FALLEN KINGDOM\nSYNOPSIS: IIn Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom, three years after the closure of Jurassic Park, a volcano about to erupt puts life on Isla Nublar at risk. With no human presence and with the dinosaurs living freely, a decision has to be made: should you return to the island to save the animals or abandon them to a new extinction?\nAUTHOR: Michael Crichton.\nAVAILABLE IN: Amazon Prime Video, Youtube and Google Play")
