a7 = ("LOGAN\nSYNOPSIS: In 2029, Logan (Hugh Jackman) makes a living as a limousine chauffeur to care for the nonagenarian Charles Xavier (Patrick Stewart). Physically weakened and emotionally drained, he is sought out by Gabriela (Elizabeth Rodriguez), a Mexican woman who needs the help of the ex-X-Men to defend little Laura Kinney / X-23 (Dafne Keen). While refusing to return to active duty, Logan is pursued by mercenary Donald Pierce (Boyd Holbrook), who is interested in the gir\nAUTHOR: James Mangold, Mark Millar\nAVAILABLE IN: Star+")
