a9 = ("THE HUNGER GAMES: CATCHING FIRE\nSYNOPSIS: The saga narrates the adventure of Katniss, a young woman chosen to participate in the 'hunger games', a kind of reality show in which a teenager from each district of Panem must fight with the others until only one comes out alive. In this episode of the series, Katniss must face strong reprisals from the local government, fighting not only for her life, but for the entire population of Panem\nAUTHOR: Suzanne Collins\nAVAILABLE IN: HBO Max, Amazon Prime Video, Youtube and Google Play")
