av1 = ("PIRATES OF THE CARIBBEAN\nSYNOPSIS:Pirates of the Caribbean (bra: Pirates of the Caribbean; prt: Pirates of the Caribbean) is a fantasy adventure film series, based on the Pirates of the Caribbean toy from Walt Disney Parks and Resorts theme parks started in 2006, directed by Gore Verbinski and Rob Marshall, written by Terry Rossio and Ted Elliott, and produced by Jerry Bruckheimer, about the adventures of Captain Jack Sparrow (Johnny Depp) and other characters such as, Will Turner (Orlando Bloom), Elizabeth Swann (Keira Knightley) , Captain Hector Barbossa (Geoffrey Rush), Joshamee Gibbs (Kevin McNally), Davy Jones (Bill Nighy), Angelica (Penélope Cruz) and Blackbeard (Ian McShane).\nAUTHOR:Terry Rossio and Ted Elliott.\nAVAILABLE IN: Disney+ and Telecine")
av2 = ("AVENGERS\nSYNOPSIS: After Thanos eliminates half of the living creatures in the entire universe, the surviving heroes must deal with the pain of losing friends and loved ones.  With Tony Stark wandering lost in space without food or water, Steve Rogers and Natasha Romanov must lead the resistance against the titan.\nAUTHOR:Anthony Russo/ Joe Russo\nAVAILABLE IN: Disney+")
av3 = ("SPIDER-MAN: NO WAY HOME\nSYNOPSIS: Spider-Man must deal with the consequences of his true identity being discovered.\nAVAILABLE IN: Amazon Prime Video, Youtube and GooglePlay")
av4 = ("WONDER WOMAN\nSYNOPSIS: Trained from an early age to be an unbeatable warrior, Diana Prince has never left the island paradise where she is recognized as a princess of the Amazons.  When pilot Steve Trevor has an accident and crashes on a local beach, she discovers that an unprecedented war is raging across the world and decides to leave her home certain she can stop the conflict.  Struggling to end the war, Diana realizes the scope of her powers and her true mission on Earth.\nAUTHOR: Patty Jenkins\nAVAILABLE IN: HBO Max, GooglePlay and Telecine")
av5 = ("VENOM\nSYNOPSIS: Journalist Eddie Brock develops superhuman strength and power when his body merges with the alien Venom.  Overwhelmed with rage, Venom tries to control Eddie's dangerous new abilities.\nAUTHOR: Todd McFarlane\nAVAILABLE IN: Amazon Prime Video, HBO Max, Youtube and GooglePlay")
av6 = ("THOR: RAGNAROK\nSYNOPSIS: Thor (Chris Hemsworth) must stop Ragnarok, the destruction of his home, Asgard, which is now under the power of the dreaded Hela (Cate Blanchett).  But the problem is that he's stuck on the other side of the universe, without his hammer, and he still has to face his former ally and avenger, Hulk, in a gladiator battle.\nAUTHOR: Eric Pearson\nAVAILABLE IN: Disney+")
av7 = ("FAST AND FURIOUS 8\nSYNOPSIS: Dom Toretto (Vin Diesel) and his crew keep slaying in their tuned cars.  But the mysterious Cipher (Charlize Theron) convinces Dom to return to life as an outlaw.  Now, the team must settle the score with Dom as they try to figure out why he betrayed his family's trust.\nAUTHOR: Chris Morgan\nAVAILABLE IN: Globoplay, Amazon Prime Video, YouTube and GooglePlay")
av8 = ("THE LOST CITY\nSYNOPSIS: Brilliant but reclusive author Loretta Sage (Sandra Bullock) writes about exotic places in her popular adventure novels, whose covers star the handsome model Alan (Channing Tatum), who has dedicated his life to impersonating the hero, Dash.  During the tour promoting her new book with Alan, Loretta is kidnapped by an eccentric billionaire (Daniel Radcliffe) so she can guide him to the treasure of the lost city described in her recent book.  In order to prove that it's possible to be a hero in real life, not just in the pages of her books, Alan sets out to rescue her.  Forced to live an epic jungle adventure, the unlikely pair must work together to survive and find the ancient treasure before it is lost forever.\nAUTHOR: Seth Gordon / Oren Uziel\nAVAILABLE IN: Paramount+")
av9 = ("DOCTOR STRANGE IN THE MULTIVERSE OF MADNESS\nSYNOPSIS: In Doctor Strange in the Multiverse of Madness, after defeating Dormammu and facing Thanos in the events of Avengers: Endgame, the Sorcerer Supreme, Stephen Strange (Benedict Cumberbatch), and his partner Wong (Benedict Wong), continue their research on the Stone of Time.  But an old friend turned enemy puts an end to his plans and causes Strange to unleash unspeakable evil, forcing him to face a powerful new threat.  The film connects with the Disney+ series WandaVision and also has a relationship with Loki.  The feature belongs to phase 4 of the MCU where the reality of the universe can collapse because of the same spell that brought the villains of the Web to the world of the Avengers and the Sorcerer Supreme will need to count on the help of Wanda (Elizabeth Olsen), who lives in isolation since the events of WandaVision.\nAUTHOR:Michael Waldron / Stan Lee\nAVAILABLE IN: Disney+")
av10 = ("MAZE RUNNER: THE DEATH CURE\nSYNOPSIS: In the third film in the saga, Thomas (Dylan O'Brien) embarks on a quest to find a cure for a deadly disease and discovers that C.R.U.E.L's plans could have catastrophic consequences for humanity.  Now, he has to decide if he will turn himself in to the C.R.U.E.L and trust the organization's promise that this will be his last experiment.\nAUTHOR: James Dashner / T.S.  nowlin\nAVAILABLE IN: Amazon Prime Video, Star+ and Disney+")
listaav = [av1, av2, av3, av4, av5, av6, av7, av8, av9, av10]  # aventura

f1 = ("THE ADAM PROJECT\nSYNOPSIS: A time traveler goes back to the year 2022 by accident and ends up meeting his younger self.  Together, and being hunted by forces from the future, the two embark on a quest to fix the timeline and save their loved ones.\nAUTHOR: Jonathan Tropper; Jennifer Flackett; T.S. Nowlin e Mark Levin\nAVAILABLE IN: Netflix")
f2 = ("THE TOMORROW WAR\nSYNOPSIS: The world is shocked when a group of time travelers arrive in 2051 to deliver an urgent message: thirty years in the future, humanity is losing a global war against a deadly alien species.\nAUTHOR: ZACH DEAN\nAVAILABLE IN: Amazon Prime Video")
f3 = ("INTERSTELLAR\nSYNOPSIS: Earth's natural reserves are coming to an end and a group of astronauts is given the mission to check possible planets to receive the world's population, enabling the continuation of the species.  Cooper is called to lead the group and accepts the mission knowing he may never see his children again.  Alongside Brand, Jenkins and Doyle, he will continue in search of a new home.\nAUTHOR: Christopher Nolan e Jonathan Nolan\nAVAILABLE IN:  HBO Max, Youtube, Amazon Prime Video and Google Play")
f4 = ("A QUIET PLACE\nSYNOPSIS: The old adage “children should be seen and not heard” has never been more true than in John Krasinski’s A Quiet Place. It isn’t a dismissive complaint from annoyed grownups; it is the key to survival against alien invaders. The first sound we hear in the film is a happy one, a kid’s toy space shuttle beaming waves of sonic joy on a bridge in the woods. It is the last noise the child will ever hear, and his helpless parents can’t even gasp in shock, or they will also be dragged into the fatal unknown. The silence is almost deafening in the 90-minute film, which only has about five minutes of dialogue. The first words are spoken about 40 minutes into the film.\nAUTHOR: Scott Beck e Bryan Woods\nAVAILABLE IN: Globoplay, Telecine, Youtube, Amazon Prime Video and Google Play")
f5 = ("SNOWPIERCER\nSYNOPSIS:In a frozen world, the last inhabitants of Earth struggle to live in a complex society inside a train that is in constant motion.\nAUTHOR:Jean-Marc Rochette; Jacques Lob e Benjamin Legrand\nAVAILABLE IN: Amazon Prime Video, Globoplay and Netflix")
f6 = ("LUCY\nSYNOPSIS: Lucy is forced to smuggle drugs into her stomach.  But the young woman's body absorbs the substances and she has superpowers, such as telepathy, telekinesis, the absence of pain and the ability to acquire knowledge instantly.\nAUTHOR: Luc Besson\nAVAILABLE IN: Netflix, Star+, Amazon Prime Video, Youtube and Google Play")
f7 = ("COLOSSAL\nSYNOPSIS: Gloria discovers she is connected to a gigantic creature that is destroying Seoul and must discover why her seemingly insignificant existence has such a colossal impact on the fate of Earth.\nAUTHOR: Nacho Vigalondo\nAVAILABLE IN: Youtube and Google Play")
